==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: noncombustible
<hw>noncombustible</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Not combustible; not able
to burn; <as>as, drapery should be made of <ex>noncombustible</ex>
materials</as>. Opposite of <ant>combustible</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> incombustible.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

